                     <interp inst="t18230219-102-person953" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . Aston sent me after the man. I saw the prisoner, and secured him - he threw the handkerchief out of his coat-pocket; I followed, and saw the boy pick it up, and gave it to me.</p>
